DESCRIPTION:Presale: € 10\,- / Doors: € 12\,- € 10\,- to € 5\,-\nonline presale\n! Birthday Special! If your birthday is on December 20th or 21st\, show your ID at the entrance and get a free ticket. Drumm n' bass\, neurofunk\nFLEXOO B2B ENERO B2B NEKU & SORA\nHAPPY HERTZ\nFENKARI B2B CRUMBLE B2B LD B2B STRYKE\nMASSIVE PLAYGROUNDS\nFPX DJ B2B HEALIAN B2B JO. NOMI B2B TWO XY\nEHRLICHES BUMBUM\nSELFLESS SOULS B2B EAZY D B2B LVKAZ\nDRUMSQUAD\nSYNERRATIC B2B VOLAINE B2B FABS\nDRUCK NACH BELIEBEN\nSPEKTURE B2B CINK B2B THE HYM B2B SNEARSTRACS\nDARK MATTER\nGet ready for an electrifying night as we welcome some top-notch Drum'n'Bass Crews to join us for a special edition! Each crew will be bringing their unique DnB flavor\, promising a sonic journey like no other. Save the date and gear up for a night of relentless beats and bass drops!
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20241220T220000Z
