DESCRIPTION:Vorverkauf: € 10\,-\nVorverkauf-Tickets\nAbendkassa: € 13\,-\nALE F\nBallroom Records\, Stripped Down Records // BRA\nhttp://soundcloud.com/alefbrazil\nB. SIDE\nPanta Rhei\nhttp://soundcloud.com/b-side-j\nFALABELLA\nFreudentanz\nhttp://soundcloud.com/djfalabella\nMARTIN FREUDENTANZ\nFreudentanz\nhttp://soundcloud.com/martinfreudentanz\nThis time we have invited Brazilian DJ and producer ALE F to the venerable Postgarage. His melodic techno\, infused with Latin rhythms\, is sure to get our hips and hearts swinging. The man from Sao Paolo regularly crosses the pond to Europe to play in clubs such as Suicide Circus\, Pacha and Grelle Forelle. This time he makes a stop in Graz - Bem-vindo. The exquisite line-up will be completed by local heroes\, whose stylistic breadth will create a beautiful musical arc throughout the night.
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20240615T210000Z
