DESCRIPTION:VVK ab € 12\,- / AK € 15\,-\nonline Presale\nTINKERHELL (Intrepid Skin\, Ones and Zeros | Buenos Aires\, Argentina)\nLISAS (The Lot Radio | New York City\, USA)\nsupported by\nFF2P [Felix Roth & DJ Vibekiller] (Violendgroove)\nBRIGHT Ø (Violendgroove)\nA Violendgroove Summer Affair𝙉𝙤 𝙝𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙨𝙨𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙃𝙤𝙢𝙤𝙥𝙝𝙤𝙗𝙞𝙖 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙎𝙚𝙭𝙞𝙨𝙢━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝘼𝙧𝙩𝙬𝙤𝙧𝙠 𝙗𝙮 𝘿𝙅 𝙑𝙞𝙗𝙚𝙠𝙞𝙡𝙡𝙚𝙧
