DTSTAMP:20260326T223223Z
DESCRIPTION:Limited Early Bird und Presale -Tickets unter www.fagtory.at\nVVK: € 15\,- erhältlich im feel free und Lustspiel\nAK: € 15\,-\nMAIN FLOOR\nShane\nhttps://www.instagram.com/dj.shane.vienna/\nTamara Mascara\nhttps://www.instagram.com/tamaramascaraofficial/\nMaukay\nhttps://www.instagram.com/maukaymusic/\n2ND FLOOR\nMischkonsum\nhttps://www.instagram.com/mischkonsum_dj/\nVanessa b2b mazid\nhttps://www.instagram.com/va_nessa_we/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/mazidopx/\nDj Wifi b2b Saya\nhttps://www.instagram.com/dj.wifi_/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/saya.techno/\nCafe\nDJ PS & Friends\nDie erste Fagtory im neuen Jahr wird magisch: Bei unserer ALLIES IN WONDERLAND-Edition entführen wir euch in die fabelhafte Welt der sexuellen Offenheit und der Toleranz\, und verwandeln die Postgarage in ein kinky Wonderland! DRESSCODE:FIERCE-FETISH-FANTASY-FAIRYTALE Packt eure märchenhaftesten und fantasievollsten Outfits aus und kombiniert sie mit euren kinky Accessoires. Ob bezaubernde:r Elf:in oder kinky Rotkäppchen – lasst euch von Märchen und Fabelwesen inspirieren. Wer sich im Fabel-Look nicht wohl fühlt\, kann wie gewohnt in kinky Kleidung kommen\, und umgekehrt. Beim Einlass wird streng auf die Einhaltung des Dresscodes geachtet – no casual Streetwear! Seid dabei\, informiert euch über unser Konzept und sichert euch eines der limitierten Tickets im Vorverkauf. Feiern wir eine märchenhafte FAGtory!
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20260110T220000Z
SUMMARY:The FAGtory Club: ALLIES IN WONDERLAND
UID:http://www.postgarage.at/program/the-fagtory-club-allies-in-wonderland_2026-01-10/
URL:http://www.postgarage.at/program/the-fagtory-club-allies-in-wonderland_2026-01-10/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:
DTSTAMP:20260326T223224Z
DESCRIPTION:€ 10\,- < 00:00 Uhr < € 12\,-\nKormos (Vienna)\nFor20 (Graz)\nLeon Mar\nMugs Bunny\nWith the second edition of our event series\, we are committed to taking the sound of the night to yet another level. Our artist selection breaks away from the ordinary\, creating space for deeper\, darker\, and groovier sounds. Our mission: to bring subtle grooves to the dancefloor and build a mood that intensifies as the night progresses. Deep grooves tap into something primal\, resonating through the body and unlocking a flow that feels instinctive and euphoric. They go beyond the surface\, creating a connection that moves you on a whole new level. Our Invites:Kormos (Vienna): A young DJ with an impressive sense for Dark Disco and Melodic House. His technical finesse allows him to seamlessly blend genres and energies\, delivering a performance that will captivate and mesmerize. For20 (Graz): Known for his relentless techno sounds\, he has already delivered a legendary closing set. This time\, he’s ready to end the night with raw energy and intense vibes once again. Kollektiv1632 Residents:Leon Mar: A lover of housey tunes with an exceptional understanding of “what the dancefloor needs.” His sets are dynamic\, emotional\, and groove driven. Mugs Bunny: Known for grooves hidden deep in the low-end\, his hypnotic rhythms and driving basslines keep the floor moving and spirits high.
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20250124T220000Z
SUMMARY:KOLLEKTIV1632 invites
UID:http://www.postgarage.at/program/kollektiv1632-invites_2025-01-24/
URL:http://www.postgarage.at/program/kollektiv1632-invites_2025-01-24/
END:VEVENT
