DESCRIPTION:Abendkassa: € 15\,-\nPresale𝙢𝙖𝙞𝙣𝙛𝙡𝙤𝙤𝙧 - 𝙙𝙣𝙗 - 𝙀𝘽𝘽\nSIMULA\n(Neksus\, UK)\nAnthropic\n(Transparent/EBB\, AT)\nEscape\n(I. ONE\, AT)\nStryke\n(Massive Playgrounds\, AT)\nTWO XY\n(Ekou/EBB\, AT)\nHost: AEL MC\n(EBB\, AT)\n𝙨𝙞𝙙𝙚𝙧𝙤𝙤𝙢 - 𝙂𝙪𝙩 𝘼𝙪𝙛𝙜𝙚𝙡𝙚𝙜𝙩\nCloud. G\n(Independent\, AT)\nJann Doll\n(Gut Aufgelegt\, AT)\nJonas Thoma\n(Independent\, AT)\nMichael High\n(Independent\, AT)\nStefan Raith\n(Gut Aufgelegt\, AT)\n𝙪𝙥𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙞𝙧𝙨 - 𝙩𝙚𝙘𝙝𝙣𝙤 - 𝙫𝙞𝙤𝙡𝙚𝙣𝙙𝙜𝙧𝙤𝙤𝙫𝙚\nFelix Roth\n(Southfirst\, AT)\nKAT ZE\n(Mahlwerk\, AT)\nMax Wagner\n(Mahlwerk\, AT)\n𝙡𝙞𝙜𝙝𝙩𝙨𝙝𝙤𝙬 𝙗𝙮 𝙫𝙞𝙨𝙞𝙤𝙠𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙚━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝙉𝙤 𝙝𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙨𝙨𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙃𝙤𝙢𝙤𝙥𝙝𝙤𝙗𝙞𝙖 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙎𝙚𝙭𝙞𝙨𝙢━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝘼𝙧𝙩𝙬𝙤𝙧𝙠 𝙗𝙮 𝙇𝙪𝙠𝙖𝙨 𝘿𝙞𝙚𝙢𝙡𝙞𝙣𝙜We proudly celebrate 10 Years of rave\, sweat and love. X Years of ehrliches BUM BUMPART TWO
