DTSTAMP:20260326T223223Z
DESCRIPTION:€ 15\,- € 10\,- €5\,-\nBirthday Special: Free entry at 31.01 & 1.02. with ID🎟️ Presale: 13€\nRobyn Chaos\nRaido\nArtist\nCink b2B Specture\nTimebox b2b Volain\nThe Hym b2b dark Fatum\nSnearstracs b2b Seraphim777\nLightshow by Feedcode64And once again\, we are proud to be the only collective in Austria carrying the true Therapy Sessions spirit forward. 💫For this edition\, we’ve prepared a fire lineup with three headliners\, guiding you through all shades of hard Drum’n’Bass — raw\, intense\, uncompromising.🔥 @robynchaosdjThe label head of Therapy Sessions Recordings herself. More than two decades ago\, she brought Therapy Session to life — and now she returns with a very special set in Graz. This is not just a booking\, it’s history meeting the present. Be ready to feel the essence of Therapy Session on the dancefloor.🔥 @raido_dnb (Darkshire)A familiar name to anyone deep into the scene. RAIDO’s sets are a journey — powerful\, precise and driven by experience. Those who’ve seen him behind the decks know: this producer knows exactly how to control the energy. We’re excited to welcome him for his first appearance in Graz.🔥 @artheist666 b2b @_seraphim777__Our local master of hard beats. Representing the raw side of the scene\, ARTHEIST completes this lineup with relentless energy and uncompromising sound — ready to stand shoulder to shoulder with the international acts. These three artists shape the atmosphere of this Therapy Sessions Austria — and we want you to be part of it. Prepare yourself. Feel the pressure. Enter the Therapy Sessions.sponsored by @makava.bio & @createtattoostudio 😘
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20260131T220000Z
