DESCRIPTION:Pre-Sale: € 13\,50\,-\navailable at https://www.darkmatterevents.at/shop\nEntry: € 15\,-\n! Birthday Special! If your birthday is on May 10th or 11th\, show your ID at the entrance and get a free ticket. GENRES: Drum'n'Bass // Neurofunk\nHEADLINERS\nProlix\n(Trendkill/Blackout)🇬🇧\nhttps://www.instagram.com/prolixdnb/\nhttps://open.spotify.com/artist/3rNP0CUzTxxuNpc3ze8rXV\nhttps://soundcloud.com/prolixuk\nSinister Souls\n(PRSPCT/Eatbrain) -SPECIAL "CHRONICLES" ALBUM RELEASE SET 🇳🇱\nhttps://www.instagram.com/sinistersouls/\nhttps://open.spotify.com/artist/6XPfY4QyCgpGvRcvHt4b7W\nhttps://soundcloud.com/sinister-souls\nSLWDWN\n(Darkshire)🇸🇰\nhttps://www.instagram.com/slwdwn_music/\nhttps://open.spotify.com/artist/3HFOgMIxcSJxLmbs2HiXba\nhttps://soundcloud.com/slwdwndnb\nSUPPORT\nSpecture\n(Dark Matter\, Therapy Sessions Austria)\nThe HYM\n(Dark Matter\, Therapy Sessions Austria)\nCink\n(Dark Matter)\nThermatical\n(Sixth Circle\, Dark Matter)\nGilgamesh\n(Drum Circle)🇵🇱\nVISUALS: Pappa Smellz (Dark. Matter/ Therapy Sessions Austria)We're turning up the volume for our project's sixth anniversary bash at the Postgarage with top-notch Drum'n'bass DJs for a night you won't forget!
