DESCRIPTION:Presale phase 2: € 13\,–Presale finale phase: € 14.-VVK-Tickets via Eventjet\nAK: € 15\,-\n1ST FLOOR HARD TECHNO\nARESKLAS\nhttps://www.instagram.com/aresklas.music/\nYOHAN. AIF\nhttps://www.instagram.com/yohan.aif/\nYØNDER b2b SCHNELLE MELLE\nhttps://www.instagram.com/yonder.techno/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/schnellemelle.techno/\nBABY BORDERLINER\nhttps://www.instagram.com/babyborderliner/\nTRYPOLAR\nhttps://www.instagram.com/dj.trypolar/\n2ND FLOOR BOUNCE\nPINK LOTION\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p1nklotion/\nSAYA\nhttps://www.instagram.com/saya.techno/\nKRAWALL JULZ\nhttps://www.instagram.com/redheadjulz/\nNAIV\nhttps://www.instagram.com/vanvanovnev/\nNZNZ X wird so stark\, dass es NZNZ 9 sofort übersprungen hat. Graz feiert den Start ins neue Jahr mit dem 10. Jubiläum seines wildesten Hardtechno-Raves am 23/01/26 in der Postgarage.2 Floors10 ArtistsX mal NZNZ✨ lights by visiokratie
