DESCRIPTION:Konzertbeginn: 20 UhrVVK via Oeticket: € 25\,–AK: € 28\,–\nThe Rural Alberta Advantage\ntheraa.com\nThe Rural Alberta Advantage is a folk-rock trio based in Toronto and made up of band members Nils Edenloff (guitar\,keyboard\,vocals)\, Amy Cole (keyboardist/bass/vocals) and Sanjeet Paul Banwatt (drums). The band has released five full length albums worldwide with Saddle Creek Records (USA/World) and PaperBag Records(Canada/World).
