DESCRIPTION:VVK ab € 10\,- | AK € 15\,-\nonline VVK-Tickets\nGROOVERIDER (Metalheadz - UK)\nSUBMOTIVE (Metalheadz - UK)\nTREX (Metalheadz - UK)\nLocal Support\nROWDIE (Schallware)\nFENKARI (Massive Playgrounds)\nMISSUKI (Schallware)\nSTRYKE (Massive Playgrounds)\nROBBE (Schallware)\nKONN:FUSED (Massive Playgrounds)\nIN. SITU (Schallware)\nHost of the Night: MC SEMLO\nGet ready for an unforgettable night of pure Drum & Bass energy as two collectives of the gradec scene Massive Playgrounds and Schallware – join forces to bring you an official Metalheadz Label Night to celebrate their 30 years anniversary. Founded by the legendary Goldie\, Metalheadz has shaped the sound of DnB for over three decades\, standing as a pillar of innovation\, raw energy\, and uncompromising quality. On July 4th\, we celebrate this legacy at Postgarage Mainfloor with a hard-hitting lineup featuring some of the most respected names in the scene\, alongside fresh talent pushing the genre forward.
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20250704T193000Z
SUMMARY:Massive Playgrounds & Schallware pres. 30 Years of Metalheadz w/ Grooverider\, Submotive\, Trex
