DESCRIPTION:VVK: € ab 10\,- | AK: € 13\,- € 14\,-\nonline Presale\nACUTUS\nANTHROPIC\nATTIC MC\nCOLFY\nDARK FATUM\nFABS\nM. A. V. E\nRESCUE\nTWO XY\nAEL MC\nARCHITACTICS\nBAROCKA\nCONCISE\nD:ENIGMA\nHEALIAN\nNEKU & SORA\nSTRYKE\nZEEP\nWe proudly present you the summer opening community rave with many of your favourite dnb collectives operating in graz!𝙉𝙤 𝙝𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙨𝙨𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙃𝙤𝙢𝙤𝙥𝙝𝙤𝙗𝙞𝙖 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙎𝙚𝙭𝙞𝙨𝙢━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝙎𝙚𝙚 𝙎𝙤𝙢𝙚𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙜 - 𝙎𝙖𝙮 𝙎𝙤𝙢𝙚𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙜
