DESCRIPTION:€ 10\,- all night long\nYUHNKI (Drumworks)\nHYPERTENSION (Beatboxx)\nGEOSTATIC (Transparent Audio / EBB)\nHEALIAN (Transparent Audio / EBB)\nCHARLY (Massive Playgrounds)\nKONN:FUSED (Massive Playgrounds)\nSTRYKE (Massive Playgrounds)\nArtwork provided by Viktoria DvoršakIt‘s been a while since EBB & MPG throw a party together. Let‘s get ready for a spontaneous Summer SessionWe proudly present YUHNKI (Drumworks) & HYPERTENSION (Beatboxx) for this edition — they're defo know how to select the right choones & introduce you into a night full of various facets of Drum&Bass!
