DESCRIPTION:AK: € 10\,– > 00:00 < € 12\,–\nCrumble\nFenkari\nMinit\nKonn:Fused\nStryke\nIllip\nLD\nCharly (Massive Playgrounds)\nMC: Semlo MC (Schallware)\nMassive Playgrounds presents: DEDICATION OF STYLEThis is not a showcase\, this is a statement. Massive Playgrounds is built on obsession – years spent chasing sound & rejecting the obvious\, digging deeper when others stop. This night is built on years of digging through crates\, broken & lost USB‘s\, late nights and sharing the same passion for the music. About learning when to hold tension & when to let it break\, about trusting selection over hype. Every resident carries a different strain of Drum&Bass – all rooted in dedication\, not trends.
