DESCRIPTION:General Admission: € 15\,–\nPresale:All branches of Steiermärkische SparkasseReduced entry for Spark7 membersand online at Eventjet & Resident AdvisorMainroom – Hard Techno & Schranz\nFELIX KRÖCHER\nsoundcloud.com/felix-kroecher\nYønder (NZNZ)\nMischkonsum (Audiotherapie)\nFelix Roth (Violendgroove)\nDJ Vibekiller (Violendgroove)\nLivkø (Oblivion)\nSideroom – Drum and Bass by EBB\nPresenting 5 Years of Transparent Audio\nAcris (AT) (Transparent Audio\, Yamatai)\nDub Ten (AT) (Transparent Audio\, Flexout\, Domain)\nYannons (NL) (Transparent Audio\, Engage Audio\, LFLF)\nsupported by:\nAnthropic (EBB)\nGeostatic b2b Two Tee (EBB / TA)\nTWO XY b2b Healian (EBB)\nHosted by AEL MCViolendgroove\, Audiotherapie\, EBB & Domnacht presentFEUER & PEITSCHE━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝙉𝙤 𝙝𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙨𝙨𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙃𝙤𝙢𝙤𝙥𝙝𝙤𝙗𝙞𝙖 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙎𝙚𝙭𝙞𝙨𝙢━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝙎𝙚𝙚 𝙎𝙤𝙢𝙚𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙜 - 𝙎𝙖𝙮 𝙎𝙤𝙢𝙚𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙜━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━Flyer Design by stylizedleo𝙥𝙖𝙧𝙩𝙣𝙚𝙧𝙨Violendgroove / Audiotherapie / Domnacht / Springfestival / Transparent Audio / EBB
