DESCRIPTION:General admission: € 14.- all night long\nPresale: starting at € 10.- | ticketstechno\nXIORRO\nRSO\, USA\nDJ MISS PARKER\nOasis\, USA\nsupport by\nBright Ø\nViolendgroove\, AT\nDJ Vibekiller [vinyl]\nViolendgroove\, AT\nFelix Roth [vinyl]\nViolendgroove\, AT\nWe invited Hör and RSO Resident 𝙓𝙄𝙊𝙍𝙍𝙊\, originally from New York\, now based in Berlin. Support by Oasis and Nowadays (NYC) Resident 𝘿𝙅 𝙈𝙞𝙨𝙨 𝙋𝙖𝙧𝙠𝙚𝙧.━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝙉𝙤 𝙝𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙨𝙨𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙃𝙤𝙢𝙤𝙥𝙝𝙤𝙗𝙞𝙖 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙎𝙚𝙭𝙞𝙨𝙢━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝘼𝙧𝙩𝙬𝙤𝙧𝙠 𝙗𝙮 𝙇𝙪𝙠𝙖𝙨 𝘿𝙞𝙚𝙢𝙡𝙞𝙣𝙜━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
