DESCRIPTION:AK € 10\,- € 13\,-\nHuebl (Nine O Nine)\nMelchiorr b2b Nepomuk (DYS Records)\nTelicho (Back to Underground)\nUrbanist (Community 1632)\nWe’re back with our second edition of Back to Underground at Postgarage – this time in collaboration with Community 1632.7 hours of relentless energy on the second floor of Postgarage. Are you ready? – VIENNA GOES GRAZHOUSE RULESNo place for homophobia\, racism\, discrimination\, or violence. We are creating a space where everyone feels safe and welcome! Timetable23:00 - 01:00 → Telicho01:00 - 03:00 → Melchiorr b2b Nepomuk 03:00 - 04:30 → Huebl 04:30 - End → Urbanist
