DESCRIPTION:Presale Ticket\nPresale starts on 28.11. for € 10\nAK: € 12 € 10 - € 5\nBirthday Special If your birthday is on December 19th or 20st\, show your ID at the entrance and get a free ticket.\nDOUBLE:UK B2B ACUTUS B2B ZETHOS (I. ONE)\nTIMEBOX B2B SNEARSTRACS B2B THE HYM B2B VOLAIN (DARK MATTER)\nHEALIAN B2B JO. NOMI B2B FPX DJ (EHRLICHES BUMBUM)\nMISSUKI B2B BHB B2B ROWDIE B2B ROBBE (SCHALLWARE)\nFENKARI B2B CRUMBLE B2B STRYKE B2B KONN:FUSED (MASSIVE PLAYGROUNDS)\nPARANRML B2B EAZY D B2B CALLISTO (DRUMSQUAD)\nBABY BIRDY B2B BABY REDLINER (BUZZ BABES)\nGet ready for a festive blast of Drum’n’Bass! This holiday season\, we’re calling in some top-tier DnB crews for a special Christmas editionEach crew brings their own signature flavor – from rolling drums to heavy bass drops – turning this night into a sonic winter journey like no otherMark the date\, grab your rave crew\, and prepare for a bass-heavy Christmas celebration that’ll shake the snow off the rooftops!► Showcases from:I. One\, Massive Playgrounds\, Ehrliches Bum Bum\, Schallware\, Drumsquad\, BuzzBabes and of course: Dark Matter
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20251219T220000Z
