DESCRIPTION:€ 10\,- € 13\,-\nDUB TEN (Empathy Audio)\ninstagram\nGEOSTATIC (Transparent Audio)\ninstagram\nSTRYKE (Massive Playgrounds)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/stryke.mpg/\nSupport by Schallware Crew\nIn. Situ\nTomkinson\nConcise\nBHB\nKylemind\nMC Han Semlo\nSCHALLWARE proudly presents WINTER FREQUENCIES\, a night of electrifying Drum and Bass that will bring the heat to Poga 2nd. We’re thrilled to welcome DUB TEN\, a heavyweight in the DnB scene\, known for delivering relentless beats and deep-packed sets. This is your chance to witness a masterclass in Drum and Bass right here in Graz! Whether you’re a dedicated DnB fan or curious about the scene\, WINTER FREQUENCIES promises a night of connection\, energy\, and unforgettable vibes.
