DESCRIPTION:Concert: 22:00\nDJ-Line: 23:30\nEntry: € 10\,-\nCOLUPAEO (live)\nhttps://colupaeo.com/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/colupaeo\nDJS OF THE NIGHT pres. by SCHALLWARE\nRowdie\nhttps://www.instagram.com/rowdie_dnb/\nLX Sounder\nhttps://www.instagram.com/lxsounder\nIn.situ\nhttps://www.instagram.com/werner.insitu/\nRobbe\nhttps://www.instagram.com/robbe_sw/\nMo’Fyah\nhttps://www.instagram.com/niko_blackwax/\nFrank Assit\nhttps://www.instagram.com/franksteel/\nConcise\nhttps://www.instagram.com/concise_sw/\nA unique summer DnB night spiced with acoustic vibes. With an exceptional Nightdrive-Music LIVE Performance by COLUPAEO.
