DESCRIPTION:€ 10\,- < 00:00 Uhr < € 13\,-\nPAXX\nLAWAL\nSOLALA\nURBANIST\nRound one in Graz! We’re excited to announce that we’ll be hosting our very first club night in Graz! In collaboration with @community_1632\, we’re introducing ourselves with a proper first dance. Expect raw\, deep\, driving\, and hypnotic grooves all night long. Also expect an intimate dance floor\, a judgment-free atmosphere\, and a space where the music always comes first. Please take care of yourself\, your friends\, and those around you. If you’re feeling unwell or uncomfortable at any time\, let our team at the entrance or bar know. We’ve got you. Come early\, stay late. You won’t regret it. We’re looking forward to seeing you\, Graz!
