DESCRIPTION:VVK: ab € 10\,- | AK: € 14\,- all night long\nOnline VVK-Ticketsmainfloor - drum and bass - EBB\nYAANO\n(Critical\, UK)\nGeostatic\n(Transparent/EBB\, AT)\nTWO XY\n(EBB\, Ekou\, AT)\nEscape\n(I. ONE\, AT)\nEnero\n(Happy Hertz\, AT)\nJO. NOMI\nHypertension\nSpecture\nThe Hym\nHost: AEL MC\n(EBB\, AT)\nsideroom - gut aufgelegt\nNina Eba\nJann Doll\nJakobo\nStefan Raith\nupstairs - techno - violendgroove - female only\nELEKTRASH\n(Argentina)\nDJ EM:PM\n(Vienna)\nVIRA66n\n(VG)\nWith summer coming to an end we are introducing club season featuring 17 acts with guests from the UK and Argentina. EBB presents a 360 Drum&Bass Floor Concept\, Violendgroove features a female only lineup upstairs. Am 2nd Floor wird gut aufgelegt.
