DESCRIPTION:AK: € 15\,–\nTicket Wave III €15.-Special DealTicket + CN Shirt €35.-Ticket + CN Hoodie €65.-https://carpe-noctem.at/tickets1st Floor Trance // Hardtechno\nVenturo\nCoach Curtis\nSisy b2b Naiv\nLivko\nMikey\nIlle\nL4NC3\n2nd Floor Drum and Bass\nConcise\nBuzz Babes\nChurcher\nCobra\nBlack State\nCallisto\nCreekz\n3rd Floor Hardgroove\nMx\nHanna Tech\nKrawall Julz\nMacak\nDj Weitsicht\n3 Floors // 20 Artists // 4 GenresTrance // DNB // Hardtechno // Hardtrance
