DESCRIPTION:Entry € 10\,- € 12\,-\nOnly 18+\nDJ SWAY (VIE)\nCOBRA (VIE)\nMXTTXM (GRZ)\nCHEFEINFACH (GRZ)\nTimetable:\nOpening - 00:30: CHEFEINFACH00:30 - 4:30: DJ SWAY // MXTTXM4:30 - closing: COBRA with a special setFOR THE LAST TIME Nur die besten Tracks von: $uicideboy$\, lil Peep\, Yeat\, Playboi Carti\, Ghostemane\, XXXTentacion\, Denzel Curry\, Yung Hurn\, lil Pump\, Zillakami\, Bladee\, Ski Mask The Slump God\, Bones\, Night Lovell\, Juice Wrld\, Trippie Redd\, Lil Uzi Vert\, Tyler The Creator\, Joji\, Pouya\, Yung Lean\, Killstation\, Fat Nick\, Shakewell\, Xavier Wulf\, A$AP Rocky\, 21 Savage\, Freddie Dredd\, Shoreline Mafia\, Craig Xen\, Chief Keef… AND MORE //// PURE ESKALATION //// WEAR ALL BLACK //// die HÄRTESTEN parties in town //// THIS IS NOT A PARTY //// THIS IS A CULT //// J O I N // T H E // C U L T //// THIS IS YOUR LAST CHANCE //
