DESCRIPTION:VVK € 12\,- / AK € 13\,-\nonline Pre-Sale - limited amount\n! Birthday Special! If your birthday is on November 15th or 16th\, show your ID at the entrance and get a free ticket. Drum'n'Bass // Neurofunk\n► HEADLINER\nBeast Jane (Darkshire)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/beast_jane\nhttps://youtu.be/4ETavvwgf8E\nBeaty (Beats for Love / III Trident)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/dj_beaty/\nhttps://youtu.be/Zetv9rNKbNM\n► SUPPORT\nANILINE (Bassfighters)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/aniline__\nCINK (Dark Matter)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/cink_darkmatter/\nAeluna (Sixth Circle)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/aelunadnb\nIZZY (Reverse)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/izzy.ndrv/\n► VISUAL MADNESS SPECIALLightshow by FEEDC0DE64 (Dark Matter)Visuals by Smellz (Dark Matter)Guided once again by the moon's gentle glow\, we have curated an extraordinary all-female DJ lineup. Each artist brings her own enchantment\, promising a night of sonic sorcery that transcends the ordinary. Our headliners\, Beast Jane (Darkshire\, CZ) and Beaty (Beats for Love / III Trident\, CZ)\, will deliver heavy bangers and mystic vibes that will leave you spellbound. Joining them are our talented support DJanes: Aniline (Bass Fighters)\, Izzy (Reverse)\, Aeluna (Sixth Circle)\, and Cink (Dark Matter). Each of these artists will weave their own magic into the night\, ensuring an unforgettable musical journey. This night promises powerful beats\, mystical atmospheres\, and music that resonates deep within. Come and be part of a celebration where the feminine spirit shines brightly.
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20241115T220000Z
SUMMARY:Dark Matter pres. WITCHCRAFT w/ Beast Jane & Beaty - All Female DJ Lineup
UID:http://www.postgarage.at/program/dark-matter-pres-witchcraft-w-beast-jane-beaty-all-female-dj-lineup_2024-11-15/
