DESCRIPTION:€ 10\,- < 00:00 Uhr < € 13\,-\nCloud. G\nhttps://soundcloud.com/claudia-guenzberg\nDino Dzafer\nhttps://soundcloud.com/dino-dzafer\nJakobo\nhttps://soundcloud.com/iakobo\nLeon Mar\nhttps://soundcloud.com/leon-rottenbacher\nMarco. T\nhttps://soundcloud.com/malextrek\nMugs Bunny\nhttps://soundcloud.com/mugsbunny\nTimB\nhttps://soundcloud.com/timbamb\nUrbanist\nhttps://soundcloud.com/theurbanist\n"Hour" is a cutting-edge house/techno event series where each artist has one hour to showcase their unique sound\, making the night full of variety and offering space for many artists and their distinctive styles.-----------------------------------------------Lights: VisiokratieArtwork and Design: Marco T. Backbone and Motivation: You
