DESCRIPTION:Presale 1st release -> € 13\,55Presale 2nd release -> € 14\,70VVK-Tickets via ra.co\nAK: € 15\,–\nMAINROOM – Drum & Bass | 11 Years of EBB\nSKANTIA (UK)\nsoundcloud.com\nGeostatic (Transparent Audio\, EBB)\nsoundcloud.com\nTWO XY (EBB)\nBuzz Babes\nFenkari (Massive Playgrounds)\nKonn:Fused (Massive Playgrounds)\nLil Zee\nSO:NA\nHosted by AEL MC & ATTIC MC\nSIDEROOM – Techno Vinyl Face 2 Face | VERZUSpresented by Violendgroove & Shockwerk\nXiorro (Ultranova)\nsoundcloud.com\nSlin (shockwerk)\nsoundcloud.com\nLex (shockwerk)\nLeo (GER)\nFelix Roth\nDJ Vibekiller\nThommy Coconut\nMischkonsum\nHosted by Referee Fetsch\nUPSTAIRS – Hard Techno | S1Brooklyn\nEVE (Vixlatixn\, JP)\nsoundcloud.com\nAdam Hadari (S1BK\, NYC)\nSeikel (S1BK\, NYC)\nWe’re Dying (S1BK\, LA)\nNinjo\n3 FLOORS | 3 STYLES | 3 CONTINENTS━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━11 YEARS OF EBB | VERZUS | S1BROOKLYNThree collectives team up to celebrate 11 years of EBB on three floors with Guest DJs from New York\, Los Angeles\, Tokyo\, London and Berlin.𝙬𝙞𝙩𝙝 𝙖 𝙩𝙤𝙩𝙖𝙡 𝙤𝙛 24 𝘼𝙘𝙩𝙨\, 𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙨 𝙞𝙨 𝙜𝙤𝙣𝙣𝙖 𝙗𝙚 𝙖 𝙣𝙞𝙜𝙝𝙩 𝙩𝙤 𝙧𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙢𝙗𝙚𝙧.𝙝𝙚𝙖𝙙𝙡𝙞𝙣𝙚𝙧𝙨 𝙤𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙧𝙚𝙚 𝙛𝙡𝙤𝙤𝙧𝙨SKANTIA / XIORRO F2F SLIN / EVE━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝙉𝙤 𝙝𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙨𝙨𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙃𝙤𝙢𝙤𝙥𝙝𝙤𝙗𝙞𝙖 - 𝙉𝙤 𝙎𝙚𝙭𝙞𝙨𝙢━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━𝙎𝙚𝙚 𝙎𝙤𝙢𝙚𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙜 - 𝙎𝙖𝙮 𝙎𝙤𝙢𝙚𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙜━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━Flyer Design by @stylizedleo𝙥𝙖𝙧𝙩𝙣𝙚𝙧𝙨EBB / Violendgroove / Shockwerk / Verzus / S1Brooklyn / Leftkiss
