DESCRIPTION:Pre Sale from € 15\,- | TICKETS at the doors: € 20\,-\nPre Sale TicketsMainfloor\ndrum & bass\nBLACK SUN EMPIRE\nblackout music\, nl\nhttps://www.instagram.com/blacksunempire_nl/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/blackout_music/\nDJ CINK\ndark matter\nFPX DJ\nehrliches bumbum\nFENKARI\nFLEXOO\nKONN:FUSED\nLD\nSTRYKE\nmassive playgrounds\nHOST OF THE NIGHT: AEL MC\n3rd floor\ntechno hosted by violend groove\nPERT\nmood\, argentina\nDJ 5KYY\nberlin\nCHRISTINA NOVA\n.\nARTWORK BY ROE\nMASSIVE FAM! Back in 2022\, we teamed up with @springfestival to bring you one of the biggest legends in the Drum & Bass game to Graz! For our 12th birthday we thought it‘s the right time to bring back BLACK SUN EMPIRE in our second living room! Get ready when the labelheads from BLACKOUT MUSIC deliver pure and unique neurofunk straight in ya face. Strong local support comes from FPX DJ\, DJ CINK & the whole Massive Playgrounds DJ Crew.
