DESCRIPTION:AK: € 10\,–\nBHB\nIN. SITU\nLX SOUNDER\nMO’FYAH\nROBBE\nROWDIE\nMC SEMLO 🎤\nVisuals by MO:YA 💡\nIt's gettin cold outside\, but it's heatin up inside 🔥 Well inna November\, we'll be keepin Postgarage 2nd floor rockin with Brazilian 🇧🇷 and Jamaican-influenced 🇯🇲 Drum & Bass 🔊 This is for the real Junglists who want to be swept away by fat basslines and toastin vocals. Light up to the rhythm and bring your Iriest I for a for truly unforgettable night 🇪🇹🦁🔥
