DESCRIPTION:VVK € 13\,- / AK € 15\,- > ab 03:00 Uhr € 10\,- > ab 04:00 Uhr € 5\,-\nonline VVK-Tickets\n! Birthday Special! If your birthday is on May 9th or 10th\, show your ID at the entrance and get a free ticket. HEADLINERS\nMerikan (Eatbrain/Blackout) ITA\ninstagram\nspotify\nsoundcloud\nTR Tactics (Blackout/Eatbrain) HUN\ninstagram\nsoundcloud\nspotify\nSUPPORT\nSpecture (Dark Matter\, Therapy Sessions Austria)\nThermatical (Dark Matter\, Sixth Circle)\nCink (Dark Matter)\nThermatical (Sixth Circle\, Dark Matter)\nDark Fatum (Dark Matter/Druck nach Belieben)\nSnearstracs (Dark Matter/Druck nach Belieben)\nWe're turning up the volume for our project's 7th anniversary bash at the Postgarage with top-notch Drum'n'bass DJs for a night you won't forget!
