DESCRIPTION:AK: € 11\,–\nVorverkauf Tickets\nBRIGHT-Ø\nInstagram\nLawal b2b Paxx\nArtifex\nInstagram\nMelchiorr b2b Nepōmuk\nThe 28th of February marks our Debut in Graz at @postgarage together with @infinitegrooves_For this night\, we’ve put together a beautiful fusion of our resident artists\, and we invited @artifex.x_ from Berlin aswell as @brightbusayo_ from Graz. Artifex is a rising DJ and producer bridging Munich and Vienna with a sound that is both raw and transcendent. Her sets move with hypnotic precision\, honoring the roots of techno while pushing its boundaries. Driven by rhythm and emotion\, Artifex crafts immersive experiences focusing on forging a deep journey within her sets. She has made her mark both locally and in international cities playing at renowned clubs such as Rote Sonne and Grelle Forelle. As she continues to evolve as an artist\, Artifex remains dedicated to the techno community by curating her own event series\, RISE\, supporting other FLINTA* artists\, being driven by a passion for music and a commitment to her craft.23:00-1:00 BRIGHT-Ø1:00-2:30 Lawal x Paxx2:30-4:00 Artifex4:00-6:00 Melchiorr x Nepōmuk
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20260228T220000Z
