DESCRIPTION:€ 10\,- all night long\nACUTUS B2B CRUMBLE [MPG\, HH]\nZETHOS B2B VNORTH [EBB]\nPANDORA [ SWITCH! ]\nFOURTEX [ SWITCH! ]\nSLOW B2B CONZEPT [DIZU\, I. ONE]\nESCAPE B2B CONCISE [SW]\nTBA B2B TBA\nHOST of the night: AEL MC [EBB]I. ONE returns to the legendary 2nd Floor of Postgarage – delivering an all-night Drum&Bass session fueled by local heavyweights from Graz and Vienna. Expect rolling basslines\, raw energy and pure Drum&Bass vibes all night long.
