DESCRIPTION:AK: € 15\,–\nAnnzie\nAvlex\nMörsen b2b Maxon\nSinny P\nStep into the world of underground House with MoreGroove\, a night designed for true music lovers and dance enthusiasts. Taking place in the iconic Postgarage Graz\, this event captures the raw\, industrial vibe of a warehouse while delivering a high-quality\, immersive sound experience. Our DJs will guide you through a journey of Minimal\, Deep Tech\, Funky House\, and Tech House\, carefully crafting hypnotic grooves\, rolling basslines\, and pulsating rhythms that keep the dance floor alive from start to finish. Every beat\, every transition\, and every drop is designed to connect you with the music and the energy of the crowd. Get ready to lose yourself in the groove with Annzie\, Avlex\, Maxon\, Mörsen\, and Skinny P. These talented DJs will take you on a journey.
LOCATION:Postgarage
DTSTART:20251122T220000Z
SUMMARY:MOREGROOVE
